                   newHabitType === 'good'
                    ? 'bg-[#ff6b35] hover:bg-orange-500 shadow-orange-500/20'
                    : 'bg-rose-600 hover:bg-rose-500 shadow-rose-500/20'
                }`}
              >
                Confirm
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      )}
    </div>
  );
};

